Hacking on Doubledown
=====================

Mac OS X
--------

Everything you need comes with 10.5 and newer.

Linux
-----

The package requires `inotify-tools` and the build process requires
`debra`, `git-core`, and `m4`.  `inotify-tools` is available in Ubuntu
10.04 Lucid Lynx.  `debra` is available from DevStructure.  `git-core`
and `m4` are available basically everywhere.

	echo "deb http://packages.devstructure.com/ lucid main" \
		>/etc/apt/sources.list.d/devstructure.list
	wget -O - http://packages.devstructure.com/keyring.gpg | apt-key add -
	apt-get update
	apt-get -y install debra git-core inotify-tools m4
